📜 Manifesto

Hello! My name is Giovanny Moreno and I enjoy creating things that live on the internet. My interest in web development started back in 2017 when my family say to me to create a website for the company, so i learned a lot about HTML & CSS!. My main focus these days is building accessible, inclusive products and digital experiences at Upstatement for a variety of clients.
